      ],
      "text": "公主请！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00021",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "将军万福。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00022",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈……妙吓，这一福，就酥了俺半边也！",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00023",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "将军乃盖世英雄，皇朝梁栋。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00024",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "不敢，拙夫不才，怎当公主称羡。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00025",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "奴家乃亡国之女，不堪侍奉宫闱。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00026",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "岂敢！公主乃金枝玉叶，凤女天孙，万望勿嫌愚夫鲁莽，万分之幸！今后内宫之事，悉听公主掌管。凡有吩咐，小将一一从命。",
      "text_length": 56
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00027",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "吓，将军，夫妇乃人伦之始，当行花烛之礼，合卺之仪，方成大礼。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00028",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "公主言之有理，仕女们撤宴过来，待俺与公主交拜天地！",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00029",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖小开门〗。定席。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00030",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "公主请！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00031",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "将军请！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00032",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖曲牌收〗。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00033",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "呀，银台上好辉煌也！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00034",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "脱布衫带叨叨令",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "银台上煌煌的凤烛燉，金猊内袅袅的香烟喷。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00035",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "和你一夜夫妻百夜恩。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00036",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "脱布衫带叨叨令",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "恁道一夜夫妻百夜恩，试问恁三生石上可有良缘分？他则待流苏帐暖洞房春，高堂月满巫山近，恁便逗上了蓝桥几层，还只怕漂漂渺渺的波涛滚。",
      "text_length": 64
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00037",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "将军请！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00038",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "脱布衫带叨叨令",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "恁道是乐煞人也么哥！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00039",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "请！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00040",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "脱布衫带叨叨令",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "又道是喜煞人也么哥！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00041",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "侍女们，看酒来，待俺回敬公主一杯。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00042",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "将军所赐，奴家敢不从命？要请将军陪奴一大杯。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00043",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "公主要俺陪一大杯，当得的，仕女们斟酒！",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00044",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "宫女甲",
        "宫女乙"
      ],
      "text": "是。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00045",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "公主请！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00046",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "将军请！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00047",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "干！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00048",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "干！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00049",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "李过吐。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00050",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "呀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00051",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "脱布衫带叨叨令",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "赤紧的蠢不剌沙叱利也学些丰和韵。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00052",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "李过醉。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00053",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "将军！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00054",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "公主，俺醉得紧了，安寝了罢！",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00055",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "侍女们辛苦了，将酒筵分散她们去罢！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00056",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "也要留几个房中服侍。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00057",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "房中自有奴家服侍，教她们去罢！",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00058",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "吖，想是公主怕羞，不好就寝。侍女们！",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00059",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "宫女甲",
        "宫女乙"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00060",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "过来谢了公主。宫女乙（同白）多谢公主娘娘。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00061",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宫女甲",
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "掌灯！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00062",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "宫女甲",
        "宫女乙"
      ],
      "text": "是。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00063",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖小开门〗。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00064",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "回避！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00065",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "宫女甲、宫女乙同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00066",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "将军今夜为何还穿此铠甲？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00067",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "不瞒公主说，一向在皇兄帐中护卫，提防奸细，日夜不能卸甲。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00068",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "如今天下已定，还虑什么奸细。况今宵乃百年喜日，岂可穿此不祥之服？",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00069",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "公主说得有理，俺正要把身子松动松动，俺唤侍女们来卸甲。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00070",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "住了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00071",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "吓？",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00072",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "待奴家亲与将军卸甲，才是妇道。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00073",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "只是劳动不当。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00074",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "好说。（脱布衫）除下了铁兜鍪凤翅嶙峋，放下了宝龙泉偷看利刃。松解了狮蛮带玉扣双扪，卸下了𤠯猊铠锁子龙鳞。",
      "text_length": 52
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00075",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "哇呀呀……",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00076",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 76,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "将军尊臂为何如此？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00077",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 77,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "不瞒公主说，前日在宁武关被遇吉打了一鞭，至今尚未痊愈。哈哈痛死我也！",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00078",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 78,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "原来如此。请将军入帐安息罢！",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00079",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 79,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "公主也早些睡罢。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00080",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 80,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "奴家除了簪珥，脱了袍服就来。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00081",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 81,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "就来吓。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00082",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 82,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "就来的。（小梁州）除下了翠翘宝髻耳珰瑱，脱却了凤衮龙氤氲。俺把那金莲儿扎凤鞋跟，防滑褪紧拴起绣罗裙。",
      "text_length": 50
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00083",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 83,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖起二更鼓〗。费贞娥（白）呀！（么篇）听听房栊寂寂悄无人，但闻得戍漏频频。（白）将军，将军呀！（么篇）我觑，觑着他眯奚醉眼醒还昏，休惊盹，心窝内宝刀抡。（白）贼子看刀！李过（白）啊呀！",
      "text_length": 92
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00084",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 84,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀。啊呀！（么篇）钢刀上冤气伸，",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00085",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 85,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李过"
      ],
      "text": "呔！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00086",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 86,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀，啊呀，呓！（么篇）银灯下冤家殒。（白）叹苍天不佑。（么篇）不能够把巨寇刃，嗳，便、便死向泉台。犹兀自含余恨，",
      "text_length": 57
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00087",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 87,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "宫女甲、宫女乙同上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00088",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 88,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "宫女甲",
        "宫女乙"
      ],
      "text": "房中为何喧嚷？我们进去看来。吓，这是二大王，为何杀死在地？想是她刺死的，拿去见大王。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00089",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 89,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "哫，谁敢？宫女乙（同白）啊呀，公主饶命㖸！",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00090",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 90,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宫女甲",
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "我非公主。宫女乙（同白）你是何人？",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00091",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 91,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宫女甲",
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "我乃费氏宫人，杀此巨寇，与君父报仇。便将我凌迟碎剐，啊呀，也不畏惧的㖸！",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00092",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 92,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "宫女甲",
        "宫女乙"
      ],
      "text": "大大王将你许配二大王也不辱没了你，亏你下此毒手！",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00093",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 93,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "嗳！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00094",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 94,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "朝天子恁道谎阳台雨云，啊呀莽巫山秦晋，可知俺女专诸不解江皋韵。俺含羞怯酬语揾泪擎樽，啊呀，遇冤家难含忍。（白）罢！",
      "text_length": 57
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00095",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 95,
      "seq_in_scene": 95,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "朝天子拚得个柳憔花翠，可也珠残玉损。啊呀早难道贪恋荣华终天恨。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00096",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 96,
      "seq_in_scene": 96,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "宫女甲",
        "宫女乙"
      ],
      "text": "拿你去见大大王就该死哩！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00097",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 97,
      "seq_in_scene": 97,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "朝天子",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "一任他碎骨粉身，一任他扬灰碾尘！今日个含笑归泉。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00098",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 98,
      "seq_in_scene": 98,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "白宫女乙",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00099",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 99,
      "seq_in_scene": 99,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "同白",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902178_e00100",
      "play_id": "70902178",
      "scene_id": "70902178_s01",
